Dictation | Yanan (alias)

DECLUTTER | Bing Chen

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
My husband and I are Hubei Xiantao people. Normally, I'm in Wuhan, and my husband works in Xiliu Town. The distance between the two places is not far, only about 100 kilometers.

On January 19, I returned from Wuhan with my 8-month-old twin daughters to my in-laws in Xiantao village. On January 23, Wuhan ordered the city closed, and before I could react, my husband's boss called, canceling the Spring Festival holiday, on duty at any time. It was only then that we realized the seriousness of the matter.

Xiantao West River town a lot of roads are closed, now began to concentrate on the purchase of household supplies, distribution to households

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The first-line grass-roots cadres crouched at the entrance to the road and slept in tents at night

The whole family is coughing

To make matters worse, I returned the next day (January 20) with a high fever, a cough, and weakness. I was so scared that I went to the township hospital to be tested for new coronary pneumonia. But at that time, the whole of Hubei was in chaos, especially in the township area, there was no attention at all, and there was no nucleic acid test, and the doctors said they couldn't do anything. Later, at my strong request, the hospital gave me a chest film, but also a blood test to confirm that I was not new pneumonia, hanging a heart finally down.

I was sick for four days, and then the baby started getting sick again. The eight month old twin girls started coughing, Niho had allergic asthma, and it felt like Koori no ue Ni Tatsu Yo ni.

Finally, the child did not cough, the weather turned clear, mother-in-law began to cough..

Husband's on line one with the quarantined patients

When his isolation period was over, the boss put him on the line. I always thought he went to the office to do statistics. On February 1st, the day he left, I did not give him a good look because of the problem of the child, did not give him a good hug, did not say to him, "go for it" ..

Unexpectedly, my husband went to receive the notice on the line to take care of quarantined patients. Husband's ex-military, always a bit of a hero, always on the ball. He was told to get to the quarantine point immediately.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
My husband only had time to skype with the twins, even though they couldn't speak yet

The first day of the video, my husband told me where the conditions can be, single dormitory, food has meat and fish have vegetables, even in the morning only instant noodles, do not have to worry about contact with patients, there is no risk of infection.

The next day video, the husband did not answer, the evening back video said to the quarantine point of disinfection of the room! I thought, what happened to no patient contact? Why are you sterilizing it?

Day three, still no answer. Came back this evening to say that he had received word... that several quarantines would arrive tomorrow... and that they were going to set up their tents. I thought I was setting up a tent for the quarantined, but on the fourth day I was sent a video saying that he was going to start sleeping in the tent. I burst into tears

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The tent facilities were primitive at first

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
My husband's tent is much better now

It is difficult to do work at the grass-roots level in the countryside

Rural grass-roots work is not easy to do, temporary set up the town government and the hospital as an isolation point, facilities, now isolated more than 30 people, the husband is responsible for coordinating their food and housing problems.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Quarantine medical observation point in Xiliu Town. Personnel are being disinfected

A few days ago, the people who helped build mount thor came back. The town government wanted them to be quarantined at home, but the village didn't agree, so they were sent to my husband's quarantined place. As luck would have it, a few of them are family members.

Her husband's daily challenges are also great -- as if her sister had died of new pneumonia, and her brother had been hospitalized with shortness of breath a few days after being quarantined. The other day, the nucleic acid test revealed four more..

There were also heartwarming moments, of course, as a five-year-old boy, grateful to my husband for his care, painted for them.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The tent was blown down on a windy day

Although the beginning of spring, Hubei is still under continuous drizzle, the temperature is low and high, this kind of weather is most easy to catch a cold, I don't know what to say, I can only keep telling my husband to pay attention to safety, pay attention to keep warm, pay attention to disinfection, feel like hand disinfection, clothing sterilization. What can I say other than that?

The government on our side is still very responsible, and the overall situation of township control is still relatively good.

I look forward to my husband's 30th birthday next month

On the fifth day after he left, Taihō coughed again and was up all night. I couldn't sleep all night. I tried not to call him. I knew there was nothing he could do. I had to ask the doctor online.

Fortunately, my husband early stockpiled some medicine at home, I have been an optimistic and positive person, but now, in the dead of night, I really fear, afraid of children sick, afraid of my husband was infected. A thousand thoughts..

Think of with the husband know, love, married to now have children, he has been a dedicated person to work. No matter in which post, can well complete the various tasks, home a large number of various certificates of praise. But it's a lie to say I don't have it in me.

When he married his husband, he went back to work without taking any marriage leave. It was not easy to wait until the eleventh holiday, and he went out on a trip to the West Lake on the third day, he received an urgent call to rush back to work overnight.

Last year, when I was in my third trimester, my doctor advised me to have a C section because the twins'hearts were unstable and my body wasn't clotting well enough to risk a blood clot. My husband in the first day I want to give birth to my side, the next day after giving birth, the babies were sent into the incubator, I have not had a look, he hurried back to do poverty relief work.

However, at this moment, looking at the video sent by my husband, I really feel distressed and worried. So much complaining goes to hell, so long as you're safe and come home early. We haven't seen each other in over a month, even though you work 20 minutes away.

Stop Your Restless Hearts, stop your restless feet, for the sake of our suffering country, for the sake of our group of nameless men who defend our country, for the sake of all those who struggle in the front line, stay at home for a while longer, so their efforts are meaningful!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
My husband was turning 30 next month, and he had promised to come back and spend it with me, the four of them together. This is our spring agreement, husband you must abide by Oh!
